data.description: (5K SELLER CONTRIBUTION TOWARDS PURCHASERS RATE BUY-DOWN OR CLOSING COSTS!) Welcome to this charming 3-bedroom, 2-bath home located in Hunstville AL on a large corner lot. Check out the Spacious Living area opening up into ther Dining room. A lovley kitchen leading to the Breakfast Area with tons of natural light. The master bedroom as a en suite bathroom, complete with a double vanity. The home also has a massive Sunroom that can be perfect space for recreation/entertaining. The backyard has a large patio along with a in ground pool perferct for family and friends to enjoy! Dont miss the opportunity to make this delighful property your own. HVAC 2021.
